 &amp; Information Network) service is used by over 260 clubs and 42,000 go=
lfers in the NYSGA's territory.</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: #000000; font-size: 10pt;"><span style=3D"caret-co=
lor: #000000;">The <strong>World Handicap System</strong> (WHS) was launche=
d in 2020 to unify six different handicap systems together into a single se=
t of Rules for Handicapping. In January of 2024, a revision came into effec=
t that will help improve the overall playing experience.</span></span></p>
